01:17:07.207 --> 01:17:08.992
Ga verder!

1187
01:17:09.993 --> 01:17:11.908
Kom binnen!

1188
01:17:11.995 --> 01:17:14.127
Wacht, mijn been.

1189
01:17:14.214 --> 01:17:16.782
Gaat het, schat?  Ben je oke?

