1265
01:21:11.234 --> 01:21:13.062
We gaan naar huis.

1266
01:21:17.414 --> 01:21:20.243
Snel, snel, kom op!

1267
01:21:20.330 --> 01:21:22.506
Oke oke.

1268
01:21:22.593 --> 01:21:24.421
